An empty template to create MVC pattern based projects with the folders tree and the files .gitignore and .htaccess already filled.

<dossier_projet_MVC> |- .gitignore |- app/ | |- Controllers/ | |- Models/ | |- Utils/ | | |- Database.php | |- Views/ | |- config.ini | |- config.ini.example | |- .htaccess -> permet de bloquer l'accès au dossier app/ |- public/ |- index.php |- .htaccess -> permet la réécriture d'URL - assets/ |- css/ |- img/ - js/


index.php filled with examples
Files added in app/Controllers and app/Models for example
